snippet.title: Xion Leak - New trailer
snippet.description:
⚡ Demo available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1948490/Xion_Leak/
👉 Wishlist it now!!

Cooperate quickly as a duo and set the fastest times to win the trophies! 🏆
Escape before the Xion gas fries your precious circuits! Run fast, be in sync, and avoid the countless dangers that the mysterious Foreman has placed in your path. 😈
